{"tid":56578,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最少兩賊在逃　操普通話疑是偷渡客　埋伏多時等劫婦孺","createTime":"2016-12-27T10:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T23:16:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d36190df737ab7c6141b9b715d6c85b252263b6","tid":56578,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:46:28.000Z","msg":"巿民行山熱點的長沙灣鷹巢山今午發生連環劫案，兩批共5名巿民先後遇上刀匪，損失現金及手機等財物。現場消息稱，最少有兩名操普通話的匪徒犯案，事後逃去無蹤。警方懷疑匪徒是非法入境者，目前有大批機動部隊警員在山上搜捕。<br />\n<br />\n今日為公眾假期，據悉鷹巢山遊人眾多，警方懷疑賊人埋伏在山上暗處，等候單獨行山人士或老弱巿民才打劫。<br />\n<br />\n首宗劫案發生於中午約12時40分，一名六旬女子獨自行經鷹巢山自然教育徑時，突然被一名賊人用左手箍頸，右手持刀指嚇事主。賊人搶去女子數十元及一部手機後離開。<br />\n<br />\n約7分鐘後，有一家四口再於案發現場附近遇上刀匪，被搶走1000元現金、一條金鏈及兩部手機。一名男子抗賊時受輕傷，但拒絕送院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161227/s00001/1482829319373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161227%2Fs00001%2F1482829319373&d=dPt5hoR%2F8%2FipJ5OUgle%2BkBpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=7f3cd6b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161227%2Fs00001%2F1482829319373&h=30f9751a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161227/s00001/1482829319373</a>"},{"pid":"af8ea7170db9c874cfc83f99d2b64c803e7ee6e9","tid":56578,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:48:27.000Z","msg":"多謝中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a1f1d9129ab869d16ca9755662bfd045331647","tid":56578,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:49:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b65f833b67ba0ade1af3a879721f08582b75ebf","tid":56578,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:23:12.000Z","msg":"97前係匪<br />\n之後以為自己有錢左<br />\n16年又變返匪<br />\n<br />\n匪性難改<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{